 </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="fr" xml:space="preserve">
            <p><supplied reason="subaudible">Autel</supplied> d'Hécate, d'Hygie, de Panacée, d'Héraklès, de <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>.</p>
         </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="en" xml:space="preserve">
            <p><supplied reason="subaudible">Altar</supplied> of Hekate, of Hygieia, of Panakeia, of Heracles, of <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>.</p>
         </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="it" xml:space="preserve">
            <p><supplied reason="subaudible">Altare</supplied> di Ecate, di Igea, di Panacea, di Eracle, di <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>.</p>
         </div><div type="commentary">
                
